Package: herringxebirdv2
Type: Package
Title: Herring x eBird Version 2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jacob", "Dingwall", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dingwalljake@gmail.com")
Author: Jacob Dingwall [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jacob Dingwall <dingwalljake@gmail.com>
Description: Outcome-blind, reproducible infrastructure for a multi-model analysis
    of Pacific herring spawn and nearshore bird responses using eBird complete
    checklists and DFO spawn records. Restricted row-level data are never bundled.
